Next Greek Bailout Loan Is Assured, Venizelos Tells To Vima

-- B y   M a r c u s   B e n s a s s o n
-- 
2011-10-01T17:35:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/next-greek-bailout-loan-is-assured-venizelos-tells-to-vima.html
Greece  is certain to receive a sixth
tranche of bailout loans under last year’s 110 billion-euro
European Union-led rescue, Finance Minister Evangelos Venizelos
told To Vima newspaper in an interview.  Greeks have taken difficult decisions and have made great
sacrifices to ensure the loan is granted, Venizelos said in the
interview published in the Athens-based newspaper today. Greeks
will continue to do what’s needed, he was quoted as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marcus Bensasson in Athens at 
 mbensasson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Petrakis at 
 mpetrakis@bloomberg.net  